## Workflows

### Preproduction Phase
- **brainstorming** - Free-form idea exploration
- **quick-brainstorming** - Fast idea generation
- **game-brief** - Define your game's vision and scope

### Design Phase
- **gdd** - Complete Game Design Document
- **narrative** - Story, characters, and dialogue
- **mvp-narrative** - Minimal viable narrative
- **art-direction** - Visual style and art direction
- **level-design** - Level and environment design

### Technical Phase
- **game-architecture** - Technical architecture document
- **project-context** - Generate project context
- **diagram** - Architecture diagrams

### Production Phase
- **sprint-planning** - Plan development sprints
- **sprint-status** - Check sprint progress
- **create-story** - Create user stories
- **dev-story** - Implement user stories
- **code-review** - Code review workflow
- **retrospective** - Sprint retrospective

### Quick Flow
- **quick-prototype** - Rapid prototype planning
- **quick-dev** - Quick implementation

### Tools
- **mind-map** - Create mind maps
- **mood-board** - Visual mood boards
- **gametest** - Test planning
- **workflow-status** - Check all workflow status

